<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Zhuhai | FarHaiWay</title>
</head>
<body class="font-sans">

  <div class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-[#006994] to-[#E0F7FA] p-8 overflow-hidden relative">
    
    <div class="absolute top-10 left-10 opacity-15 pointer-events-none transform scale-150 origin-top-left z-0">
      <svg width="200" height="150" viewBox="0 0 300 200" fill="#F4E4BC">
        <polygon points="50,20 60,45 85,45 65,60 75,85 50,70 25,85 35,60 15,45 40,45" transform="scale(1.5) translate(10, 15)" />
        <polygon points="50,20 60,45 85,45 65,60 75,85 50,70 25,85 35,60 15,45 40,45" transform="scale(0.5) translate(280, 20) rotate(20)" />
        <polygon points="50,20 60,45 85,45 65,60 75,85 50,70 25,85 35,60 15,45 40,45" transform="scale(0.5) translate(340, 70) rotate(40)" />
        <polygon points="50,20 60,45 85,45 65,60 75,85 50,70 25,85 35,60 15,45 40,45" transform="scale(0.5) translate(340, 140) rotate(0)" />
        <polygon points="50,20 60,45 85,45 65,60 75,85 50,70 25,85 35,60 15,45 40,45" transform="scale(0.5) translate(280, 190) rotate(-20)" />
      </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="absolute -left-10 -bottom-10 opacity-40 pointer-events-none transform scale-110 z-0">
      <svg width="300" height="400" viewBox="0 0 100 140" fill="none" stroke="#9DC183" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <path d="M45 140 Q30 80 45 30" /><path d="M55 140 Q40 80 45 30" /><path d="M42 120 L52 120" /><path d="M39 100 L49 100" /><path d="M38 80 L46 80" /><path d="M40 60 L45 60" /><path d="M42 45 L46 45" />
        <path d="M45 30 Q15 10 0 35" /><path d="M45 30 Q80 15 95 30" /><path d="M45 30 Q10 40 5 70" /><path d="M45 30 Q85 45 85 75" /><path d="M45 30 Q25 65 30 90" /><path d="M45 30 Q65 65 60 90" /><path d="M45 30 Q45 -5 60 10" />
      </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="absolute -right-10 -bottom-10 opacity-40 pointer-events-none transform scale-110 -scale-x-100 rotate-6 z-0">
      <svg width="300" height="400" viewBox="0 0 100 140" fill="none" stroke="#9DC183" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <path d="M45 140 Q30 80 45 30" /><path d="M55 140 Q40 80 45 30" /><path d="M42 120 L52 120" /><path d="M39 100 L49 100" /><path d="M38 80 L46 80" /><path d="M40 60 L45 60" /><path d="M42 45 L46 45" />
        <path d="M45 30 Q15 10 0 35" /><path d="M45 30 Q80 15 95 30" /><path d="M45 30 Q10 40 5 70" /><path d="M45 30 Q85 45 85 75" /><path d="M45 30 Q25 65 30 90" /><path d="M45 30 Q65 65 60 90" /><path d="M45 30 Q45 -5 60 10" />
      </svg>
    </div>

    <nav class="relative z-30 flex justify-between items-center text-[#F4E4BC]">
      <label for="menu-toggle" class="text-3xl font-bold cursor-pointer hover:text-white select-none">☰</label>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col items-end gap-2 font-bold">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
            <a href="/" class="hover:underline">Home</a>
            <a href="/china" class="hover:underline">China</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex gap-4 border border-[#F4E4BC]/30 p-1 px-3 rounded-full text-sm bg-[#006994]/20 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <label for="lang-en" class="cursor-pointer hover:underline peer-checked/en:text-white select-none">EN</label>
          <label for="lang-th" class="cursor-pointer hover:underline peer-checked/th:text-white select-none">TH</label>
          <label for="lang-ch" class="cursor-pointer hover:underline peer-checked/ch:text-white select-none">CH</label>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <input type="checkbox" id="menu-toggle" class="peer/menu hidden">
    <div class="hidden peer-checked/menu:block absolute top-28 left-8 z-30 bg-[#F4E4BC] p-6 rounded-lg text-[#006994] shadow-xl w-48 border border-[#F4E4BC]/50">
      <ul class="space-y-4 font-bold text-lg">
        <li><a href="/china/guangzhou" class="hover:text-black block">Guangzhou</a></li>
        <hr class="border-[#006994] opacity-30 my-2">
        <li><a href="/gallery" class="hover:text-black block">Full Gallery</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[70vh] text-center mt-4">
      
      <input type="radio" name="language" id="lang-en" class="peer/en hidden" checked>
      <input type="radio" name="language" id="lang-th" class="peer/th hidden">
      <input type="radio" name="language" id="lang-ch" class="peer/ch hidden">

      <div class="hidden peer-checked/en:flex flex-col items-center">
        <h1 class="text-7xl font-bold text-[#F4E4BC] drop-shadow-md">Zhuhai</h1>
        <p class="text-2xl text-[#E0F7FA] mt-4 font-medium tracking-wide">Life in the City of Islands</p>
        
        <div class="max-w-2xl mt-12 bg-white/10 p-8 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 text-white text-left shadow-lg">
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
            I have been living in Zhuhai since 2024. I love the hot seasons here; they match the coastal energy perfectly. 
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            I'll admit I hate the cold season of Zhuhai, even though it's not actually that cold. Overall, it's a very chill city, but it has fun, bustling neighborhoods for when I want to get out and have a drink.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hidden peer-checked/th:flex flex-col items-center">
        <h1 class="text-7xl font-bold text-[#F4E4BC] drop-shadow-md">จูไห่</h1>
        <p class="text-2xl text-[#E0F7FA] mt-4 font-medium tracking-wide">ชีวิตในเมืองแห่งหมู่เกาะ</p>
        
        <div class="max-w-2xl mt-12 bg-white/10 p-8 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 text-white text-left shadow-lg">
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
            ฉันอาศัยอยู่ในจูไห่มาตั้งแต่ปี 2024 ฉันชอบฤดูร้อนที่นี่มาก มันเข้ากับบรรยากาศเมืองชายฝั่งได้เป็นอย่างดี
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            ฉันสารภาพเลยว่าเกลียดฤดูหนาวของจูไห่ ถึงแม้ว่าจริงๆ แล้วมันจะไม่ได้หนาวขนาดนั้นก็ตาม โดยรวมแล้วที่นี่เป็นเมืองที่ชิลล์มาก แต่ก็มีย่านที่คึกคักและสนุกสนานสำหรับเวลาที่ฉันอยากออกไปดื่มสังสรรค์
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hidden peer-checked/ch:flex flex-col items-center">
        <h1 class="text-7xl font-bold text-[#F4E4BC] drop-shadow-md">珠海</h1>
        <p class="text-2xl text-[#E0F7FA] mt-4 font-medium tracking-wide">百岛之市的生活</p>
        
        <div class="max-w-2xl mt-12 bg-white/10 p-8 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 text-white text-left shadow-lg">
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
            我从2024年开始住在珠海。我非常喜欢这里的炎热季节，非常契合这座海滨城市的活力。
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            不得不承认，我很讨厌珠海的寒冷季节，尽管其实并没有那么冷。总的来说，这是一座非常悠闲的城市，但当我想要出去喝一杯时，这里也有非常繁华热闹的街区。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
